    Hahn and Hansen (1991)

    hahn_1991.Rd

    Allometric models from Hahn and Hansen (1991)

    Stem Volume Models

    vsa = b_1 * hstix^b_2 * (1 - exp(b_3 * dsob^b_4))

    • vsa [ft3] - volume of the entire stem, including top and stump

    • hstix [ft] - Site index at an un-specified base age.

    • dsob [in] - diameter of the stem, outside bark at breast height
